---
import BeliefCard from "../../components/BeliefCard.astro";
import ImageHeader from "../../components/ImageHeader.astro";
import YouthEventCard from "../../components/YouthEventCard";
import youthImage from "../../images/pages/youth.jpg";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Lone Rock Youth Group">
  <ImageHeader title="Lone Rock Youth Group" image={youthImage} />

  <div class="container mx-auto p-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
      <BeliefCard name="You Belong Here">
        Looking for a place to have fun, make friends, and grow your faith? The
        Lone Rock Bible Church Youth Group has it allâ€”games, laughter, weekly
        Bible studies, and tons of opportunities to connect with other teens
        just like you. Come join us and see what we're all about! Everyone age
        12 through high school is welcome!
      </BeliefCard>

      <BeliefCard name="Connect">
        We're more than just a youth group; we're a close-knit community where
        friendships are built through shared experiences and awesome activities.
        Whether you're into games, music, or just hanging out, there's always
        something exciting happening here. Our weekly Bible studies are
        laid-back and real, diving into topics that matter to you and help you
        live out your faith every day.
      </BeliefCard>

      <BeliefCard name="Stay Up To Date">
        Stay in the loop with everything happening in our youth group! The
        latest updates, events, and activities are always posted right here on
        this page, so you'll never miss out on what's coming up. We'll keep you
        informed about upcoming game nights, special outings, service projects,
        and any changes to our weekly Bible studies. Whether you're planning
        your week or looking for something fun to do, you can always count on
        this page to have the latest info. Be sure to bookmark it and check back
        regularly, because there's always something new and exciting in the
        works!
      </BeliefCard>

      <BeliefCard name="Stay In Touch">
        Want to get on our text reminder list? Need to talk to us? Prayer
        requests? We've got you covered!
        <p>Text Us: <strong>1-833-267-8235</strong></p>
        <p>
          Email Us: <strong
            ><a href="mailto:lucas@lonerockbiblechurch.com">Lucas Pernsteiner</a
            ></strong
          >
        </p>
      </BeliefCard>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto mt-5 flex justify-center items-center">
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
      <YouthEventCard client:visible />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
